{"tid":1184061,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有拍拖就唔好再同異性講心事","createTime":"2019-06-03T11:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-05T14:21:19.000Z","uid":58333,"like":80,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"2a0b38abe8dd8fbbcfe95a457a4e64ebfbc47233","tid":1184061,"uid":58333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:38:25.000Z","msg":"其實一講完心事 就會覺得同果個人close咗好多 相信呢種感覺大家都試過<br />\n<br />\n而當你有拍拖 仲同異性講心事既話<br />\n不知不覺間 會依賴咗呢個人<br />\n不知不覺間 會覺得呢個人好識得安慰自己<br />\n不知不覺間 會覺得呢個人好可靠 好似永遠係背後支持自己咁<br />\n不知不覺間 就會覺得身邊果件無用 即使佢有用 你都會覺得佢無用 因為你根本無同過佢分享你既心事 佢又有咩機會進入你內心 去幫你呢?<br />\n不知不覺間 就會大事小事都第一個走去同佢分享<br />\n不知不覺間 就會慢慢鍾意咗呢個人<br />\n不知不覺間 同另一半距離會愈黎愈遠 感情就會愈黎愈差<br />\n最後 綠帽大放送<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實一開始未必係專登故意帽人<br />\n只係當你不斷同異性傾心事 慢慢人地走咗入你個心 而你自己都唔會知 係唔會知呀!<br />\n所以你會覺得同異性講心事唔係帽緊人 但其實已經係!<br />\n<br />\n以前ex就係成日同異性講心事 漸漸開始就無再同過我講 有啲心事仲要係關於我 佢成日係我背後同佢地講我 都唔直接同我講 唔肯同我溝通<br />\n最後 帽咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以各位要好好睇實自己另一半<br />\n唔好以為佢地同異性講心事係小事 <br />\n其實係好大件事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap_2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/green_cap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3715f3a6eccb03833782374ef90785b337cb1eb8","tid":1184061,"uid":14392,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:41:53.000Z","msg":"好似幾中，但係因咩事對方唔同你傾心事？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba7c282e9945eb6d8541b7cd90823c41800778b","tid":1184061,"uid":67598,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:44:56.000Z","msg":"管得住先得咖，叫對方避忌啲，又話都冇野，冇野冇野最後咪有野<br />\n同人有野仲要話我成日管佢先要同人地傾計，搵同性傾唔得既咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ee35669dddc0f63b950a8159c7cadafadc8a4d","tid":1184061,"uid":228963,"like":6,"dislike":4,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:45:12.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"688500d6afed7b2f88943dd5617824bfab9408b3","tid":1184061,"uid":185066,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:47:04.000Z","msg":"其實我覺得可以並存 你對傾訴果個人產生感情係因為你心唔夠定 啫係你唔夠鐘意你現任 如果唔係 朋友同情人既界線一定係分得清"},{"pid":"d87552e5a7f5b9e9eade27ce58dcc78049dcfbc5","tid":1184061,"uid":67280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"樓上一個狗公同一隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d9e99678f4356ee15fd09d6e58c582712e570c3","tid":1184061,"uid":64601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"d87552e5a7f5b9e9eade27ce58dcc78049dcfbc5","tid":1184061,"uid":67280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T11:58:12.000Z","msg":"樓上一個狗公同一隻雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:11:19.000Z","msg":"係咪#3？"},{"pid":"d62e6aa156b44b9699a5263cab001bc005763eb6","tid":1184061,"uid":231583,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:25:11.000Z","msg":"有講得心事既異性好朋友都唔得？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個堆不知不覺只係本來就有出軌DNA既人先會做既事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ebe55b5677f5b128dbcb8d83c21ba30b3e30ce2","tid":1184061,"uid":49575,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:30:34.000Z","msg":"避忌係基本尊重<br />\n想要人做好基本野先要做好自己"},{"pid":"8d0e004db3889bc996bf0531a357e883fc9589cb","tid":1184061,"uid":209120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-03T12:31:42.000Z","msg":"傾心事?收兵咋<br />\n做情緒垃圾桶做得你咁開心"},{"pid":"67274f4c4ae0621f759820e95e4e9cfcf3131893","tid":1184061,"uid":73066,"like":2,"dis